Delve into the renowned classics of open-world survival with the original S.T.A.L.K.E.R. trilogy, now available to console players for the first time ever!

S.T.A.L.K.E.R.: Shadow of Chornobyl
The forerunner of the open-world survival FPS genre, the classic S.T.A.L.K.E.R. — recalibrated for a console journey. Dive into the grim atmosphere of this dark science-fiction world on a path to Chornobyl in the first chapter of the original trilogy.

S.T.A.L.K.E.R.: Call of Prypiat
A military expedition to the center of the Zone has mysteriously disappeared. Your task, as a special service operative in S.T.A.L.K.E.R.: Call of Prypiat – the final part of the original trilogy, is to figure out the reason behind the disappearance and determine the status of the personnel. This edition has been recalibrated for a journey on console.

S.T.A.L.K.E.R.: Clear Sky
Great Emission, the biggest anomalous energy blowout from the times of Second Incident at The Chernobyl Nuclear Power Plant, has shaken the world again and reshaped the Zone. To investigate its cause and and prevent future cataclysms is your only chance to survive in S.T.A.L.K.E.R.: Clear Sky.

    Ash, an O.C.U. soldier, survives the initial assault, but soon finds himself caught in a battle to escape Alordesh, now controlled by the Revolutionary Army. As Ash and his comrades navigate the chaotic underground, they uncover a massive conspiracy behind the rebellion.

description:
Japanese Original Edition, Scarlet & Violet Expansion Pack

The upcoming Japanese High Class Pack set, SV8a Scarlet & Violet Terastal Festival, has been officially revealed on the official Japanese Pokemon Card Game YouTube channel during the DREAM MATCH2024 livestream. This is the final set of 2024 for Japan.

Similar to most High Class Pack sets, this particular High Class Pack set includes numerous reprinted and competitively used cards featuring new and old artwork. Every booster pack guarantees 1 ex card.

New cards revealed are Flareon ex, Eevee ex, Hoothoot & Larry's Professionalism.

The booster pack artwork feature Stellar type Umbreon & Glaceon, indicating that these might get an ex card too in this set.

Set Contains:

  • 10 Packs/Box
  • 10 Cards/Pack 
  • (Cards are randomly enclosed)

description:

Dive into the action-packed world of Dragon Ball with the Dragon Ball Super Divers Card Game. This exciting trading card game allows players to engage in epic battles, strategize with iconic characters, and unleash powerful attacks inspired by the legendary anime series. Featuring a wide array of characters, from Saiyans to powerful deities, the game offers endless possibilities for fans to build their ultimate deck and compete against others. Whether you're a seasoned player or new to the game, the Dragon Ball Super Divers Card Game provides an immersive experience that captures the intense spirit of Dragon Ball.

Introducing the Ultimate Diver Box for the Dragon Ball Super Divers Card Game—crafted for true enthusiasts who seek the pinnacle of gameplay and collection. This exclusive box is packed with an array of premium cards, featuring powerful abilities and rare, sought-after characters that can elevate any deck to new heights. The Ultimate Diver Box includes three Advanced Packs, seven luxurious battle cards, and an avatar card, giving you everything you need to build a formidable deck. With 11 refill sheets included, the box can store up to 99 cards, making it as functional as it is impressive. Perfect for competitive players aiming to dominate the game and collectors looking to add the most coveted cards to their collection. With its exceptional design and top-tier content, the Ultimate Diver Box is a must-have for any dedicated Dragon Ball Super Divers Card Game fan who demands the very best.

1 set: 1 binder (foil specification), 11 9-pocket refills, 7 original battle cards, 1 original avatar card, 30 original sleeves, 3 advance packs.

This set of palm-sized plush mascots from the Celebi Celebration Series, created to celebrate the reopening of the Pokémon Center Nagoya, features Pikachu enjoying some of Nagoya’s most famous dishes! These adorable plush mascots are perfect for fans who want to celebrate Pikachu's foodie adventure in Nagoya.
